College basketball player Lauren Hill lost her battle with cancer on Friday morning .
The Indiana native , who was diagnosed with a rare form of brain cancer shortly after her 18th birthday , defied doctors told her that she would not live past December .
Instead she played four games with her team at Mount St. Joseph University in Cincinnati and raised more than $ 1.5 million for research into the cancer , Diffuse Intrinsic Pontine Glioma .
